  "title": "IT Support Engineer (SQL / Network Switches / Training provided)",
  "description": "<p><strong>• Well Established Company</strong><br /><strong>• Salary: $3000 - $3700 + $300 Allowance</strong><br /><strong>• Working hour: 8.30am – 5.30pm (Monday - Friday)</strong><br /><strong>• Working Location: Islandwide• Variable bonus + Excellent Wellfare</strong><br /><br /><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Install, configure, and troubleshoot <strong>Windows Server 2019</strong> to ensure stable and secure system operations.</li><li>Perform <strong>basic SQL queries</strong> for database management, reporting, and data validation.</li><li>Set up, maintain, and troubleshoot <strong>factory network switches</strong>, ensuring reliable network connectivity.</li><li>Support system and network operations in an <strong>industrial / production environment</strong>.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Background in cyber security practices to enhance system protection and data integrity</li><li>Possess experience working with Linux systems and virtual machines (VMs) in a networking environment will be an added advantage</li><li>0 - 2 years of relevant working experience in similar position</li></ul><p><br />Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume:<br /></p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p><br />We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br />YEOW CHANG FU (R23118759)<br />EA Recruitment Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
